headline: 3 Top Dividend Stocks to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: When those down years come, it can be comforting to have a portfolio full of businesses that pay consistent dividends to their shareholders.  Here's why they like Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO), Home Depot (NYSE: HD), and Realty Income (NYSE: O).  John Ballard (Coca-Cola): Coca-Cola has paid a growing dividend for 62 years, making it one of the most time-tested dividend investments for the long haul.
